Wenger is nothing if not a stubborn fighter and he reminded his critics that he has always honoured his contracts. There has been the suggestion that his position could be reviewed at the end of the season but Wenger knows he has the security of a deal until the summer of next year.<br />
<br />
&ldquo;Will I be here? My contract clarifies that,&rdquo; Wenger said. &ldquo;Did I ever walk away? Never. Why should I change?&rdquo;

